@startuml C4_Pattern_AgentInvocation
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Component.puml

title YAWL Workflow Pattern - Autonomous Agent Invocation

Boundary(yawl, "YAWL Workflow") {
    Component(agent_task, "AgentTask", "Task", "Invoke agent")
    Component(agent_config, "AgentConfig", "Config", "Agent details")
}

Boundary(protocol_layer, "Protocol Layer") {
    Component(mcp_client, "MCPClient", "MCP", "Claude agents")
    Component(a2a_client, "A2AClient", "A2A", "Z.AI agents")
    Component(protocol_switch, "ProtocolSwitch", "Router", "Select protocol")
}

Boundary(agent_execution, "Agent Execution") {
    Component(agent_context, "AgentContext", "State", "Execution context")
    Component(task_spec, "TaskSpec", "Spec", "What to do")
    Component(result_handler, "ResultHandler", "Outcomes", "Collect results")
}

Boundary(external_agent, "External Agent") {
    Component(mcp_agent, "Claude Agent", "LLM", "MCP-enabled")
    Component(a2a_agent, "Z.AI Agent", "Engine", "A2A-enabled")
}

agent_task --> agent_config: Uses config
agent_config --> protocol_switch: Selects protocol
protocol_switch --> mcp_client: If MCP
protocol_switch --> a2a_client: If A2A

mcp_client --> agent_context: Sends context
a2a_client --> agent_context: Sends context
agent_context --> task_spec: Describes task
task_spec --> mcp_agent: Invokes
task_spec --> a2a_agent: Invokes

mcp_agent --> result_handler: Returns result
a2a_agent --> result_handler: Returns result
result_handler --> agent_task: Completes

Note as N1
Agent Invocation:
- MCP: Claude Code agents
- A2A: Z.AI autonomous agents
- Context: Workflow state + task description
- Result: Agent output (structured JSON)

Example: "Review expense report and approve if <$1000"
End note

SHOW_LEGEND()
@enduml
